  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">Dialog: Function-Block: Motion-Path</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Heading2" style="page-break-before:always;">Motion-Path FB</para>
    <para styleclass="SeeAlso">see <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Command-AddFBMotionPath">Add Motion-Path FB</link></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#343400;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="VariableName">IMPORTANT<text styleclass="Heading4 Toggle_atocs_">:</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text Howindent4bullets">Motion-values at the input to a </text><text styleclass="Element-Header">Motion-Path FB</text><text styleclass="Body Text Howindent4bullets"> control the motion of a </text><text styleclass="VariableName">Motion-Point</text><text styleclass="Body Text Howindent4bullets"> along a sketch-path.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text Howindent4bullets">The motion-values at the input </text><text styleclass="VariableName" style="color:#ff0000;">must</text><text styleclass="Body Text Howindent4bullets"> be </text><text styleclass="VariableName">Linear</text><text styleclass="Body Text Howindent4bullets"> or </text><text styleclass="VariableName">Rotary</text><text styleclass="Body Text Howindent4bullets"> - see also </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Dialog-FunctionBlock-Motion" anchor="DIALOG-MOTIONFB-PARAMETERS" styleclass="Body Text Howindent4bullets">Motion FB dialog</link></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text Howindent4bullets">When the </text><text styleclass="VariableName">Data-Type</text><text styleclass="Body Text Howindent4bullets"> at the input is:</text></para>
    <list id="0" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="VariableName">Linear</text>, <text styleclass="Body Text HowTo">the linear position of the </text><text styleclass="Interface">Motion-Point</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo"> along the sketch-loop = </text><text styleclass="VariableName">Linear motion-value</text><text styleclass="BodyText BI">*</text></li>
      <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="VariableName">Rotary</text><text styleclass="Body Text">, </text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo">the linear position of the </text><text styleclass="Interface">Motion-Point</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo"> along the sketch-loop = </text><text styleclass="VariableName">Angular motion-value</text><text styleclass="BodyText BI">*</text><text styleclass="VariableName"> × (total length of sketch-loop / 360)</text></li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="BodyText BI">* </text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo">See also </text><text styleclass="Parameter">Linear Offset</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo"> and </text><text styleclass="Parameter">Phase Offset</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> parameters - </text><text styleclass="SeeAlso">see </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="" anchor="MotPathPtPara" styleclass="SeeAlso">here</link></para>
    <para styleclass="SeeAlso">See more <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="" anchor="MotionRangeMotionFB">Data-Type and Motion-Points</link></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#343400;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading4 Toggle_atocs_">How to open the Motion-Path dialog</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="1" colcount="2">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:40px;">
          <para styleclass="Interface" style="text-align:right;"><image src="MD-Icon-FB-MotionPath.png" scale="100.00%" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Body Table">To open the<text styleclass="Element"> Motion-Path dialog</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Block" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td style="border-top:none; border-right:none; border-bottom:none;">
                <list id="1" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="B Bullets" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
                  <li styleclass="B Bullets"><text styleclass="Body Text">Double-click the </text><text styleclass="Element" style="font-size:10pt;">Motion-Path FB</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> in the graphics-area</text><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
                </list>
                <para styleclass="Interface2">OR</para>
                <list id="2" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="B Bullets" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
                  <li styleclass="B Bullets"><text styleclass="SeeAlso">See </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Dialog-How-to-Open-a-Dialog-Box" styleclass="SeeAlso">How to Open a dialog</link><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
                </list>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text">The <text styleclass="Element-Header">Motion-Path dialog</text> is now open.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#343400;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text"><anchor id="DIALOG-MOTIONPATHFB" styleclass="Heading3_atocs_"><keywords><keyword>Motion-Path FB<keyword>Dialog box</keyword></keyword><keyword>Dialog<keyword>Motion-Path FB</keyword></keyword></keywords></anchor><text styleclass="Heading3_atocs_"> Motion-Path dialog</text></para>
