                <para styleclass="Body Text">If you change <text styleclass="Parameter">Number of Motion-Points</text><image src="Red-14-1b.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text style="font-style:italic;">&#32;</text><text style="font-style:normal;">parameter, you </text><text styleclass="VariableName" style="color:#ff0000;">must</text><text style="font-style:normal;"> c</text>lick the button to generate <text styleclass="Interface">Motion-Points.</text>&#32;</para>
