                <para styleclass="Body Text">Then, as you edit the <text styleclass="Parameter">Control-Dimension,</text> the shape of the <text styleclass="VariableName">sketch-loop</text> is more predictable - <text styleclass="SeeAlso-small">see Note 1</text>&#32;</para>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
        </td>
