          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">The default values for the <text styleclass="Parameter">Control-Dimension </text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;">Min</text> or <text styleclass="Parameter-Header" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;">Max</text> are such that the <text styleclass="Parameter">Actual-Path Length</text> can be equal to the <text styleclass="Parameter">Target Path Length. </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">However, it is possible that the <text styleclass="VariableName">Root-Finding Math</text> is confused!</para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">To reset the <text styleclass="VariableName">Root-finding Math</text>:</para>
          <list id="14" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted">Increase or decrease the <text styleclass="Parameter">Control-Dimension Min/MAX</text><text styleclass="Body Text">, then try to edit</text> the <text styleclass="Parameter">Target-Path-Length</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> again.</text></li>
            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="Body Text">You may need to edit these values to be almost equal to the actual length of the </text><text styleclass="Parameter">Control-Dimension</text><text styleclass="Body Text">.</text></li>
