          <para styleclass="Body Table">The motion of <text styleclass="Interface">Motion-Points</text> along the <text styleclass="VariableName">sketch-loop</text> is a function of the <text styleclass="VariableName">Data-Type</text> at the input-connector to the <text styleclass="Element">Motion-Path FB</text>. </para>
          <para styleclass="Body Table">The <text styleclass="VariableName">Data-Type</text> at the input-connector <text styleclass="VariableName" style="color:#ff0000;">must</text> be <text styleclass="Parameter">Linear</text> or <text styleclass="Parameter">Rotary</text><text styleclass="VariableName">.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Table"><text style="font-size:12pt;">&#32;</text><text styleclass="ParameterHeader">Data-Type =</text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Interface2" style="color:#ff0000;">Linear</text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;">&#32;</text></para>
